verbose_text: In addition, out of five studies [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR], three studies reported significant differences between HCC patients and cirrhotic patients (lowered level in one study and elevated level in two studies), and out of two studies [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR] reporting serum IL-8 level in patients with HCC compared to patients with CH, both studies reported an elevated level of IL-8.
